  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the action is to improve access to potable water and sanitation facilities, to enhance environmental sanitation and to improve hygiene practices of 455,000 conflict-affected men, women and children in KP and FATA through installation/rehabilitation of water points, latrines, handwashing pads, solid waste disposal schemes, distribution of hygiene kits and hygiene awareness.</narrative>
